  * Karya Market — PyQt6 theme/plugin marketplace browser
  * Custom kernel PKGBUILDs (linux-karya + linux-karya-hardened)
  * All Python/Shell/PKGBUILD/QML syntax verified
  * Unicode escape bug fixed permanently
  * Docker Compose / Kubernetes Helm / Ansible deployment support

